. Named after Prof. Dr Vladimir Pešić (
<collectingCountry id="EADBE2FEFFFEFFC9FCFFFC96398AF82C" box="[769,913,799,825]" name="Serbia" pageId="2" pageNumber="145">Montenegro</collectingCountry>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="9273A26EFFFEFFC9FF39FCCB3BF2F848" blockId="2.[151,1437,150,897]" box="[199,489,834,861]" pageId="2" pageNumber="145">
<emphasis id="A0B87E7CFFFEFFC9FF39FCCB3B31F849" bold="true" box="[199,298,834,860]" pageId="2" pageNumber="145">Habitat.</emphasis>
Running waters.
</paragraph>
